Umm you have some major things confused. 
 First haste items just say (haste) they are not spell haste, that is completely different.

second you may only have one item, one spell and one bard song active at once, any others will not stack.

there is one exception to the one spell rule, Speed of Vallon will stack with Celerity, one being enchanter the other shaman cast, these are the only two that i know of that will do this.

Spell haste refers to the speeding up of casting, and it is not clickable it is a permanent effect.

The haste cap is either 84% or 85% not sure which, and only 2 or so lower level bard songs can break the cap.


